    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including data retrieval, conditional logic, and error handling. It executes several other stored procedures and updates multiple tables, which adds to its complexity. However, it does not involve complex calculations or intricate data transformations, keeping the complexity at a medium level."
        }
